        <item>
          <title>BYU sweeps men's and women's cross-country national titles</title>
          <description><![CDATA[WACO, Tex. (ABC4 Sports) - BYU became just the fifth school ever to win national titles in both men's and women's cross-country. The #1 ranked women's team won its sixth in program history, with a team score of 147 at the Zimmer Championship Course Saturday morning.]]></description>
